#ROBOT FRAMEWORK
--> it is generic test automation framework for acceptance testing
--> it has easy to use tabular syntax which utilizes the keyword-driven testing approach
--> libraries implemented either with python or java

#ADVANTAGES OF ROBOT FRAMEWORK
1. Free Open Source
2. Simple Tabular Syntax/easy syntax
3. fast development with minimum coding efforts
4. Default reports with detailed information
5. detailed logs
6. generic test libraries/lots of libraries/allow to extend libraries
7. web testing,swing,SWT,Windows GUI,databases,SSH,Telnet etc
8. distributes structure

#API TESTING TESTING USING ROBOT FRAMEWORK
**Installation Process***
1.setup python
2.setup pycharm
3.setup intellibot plugin - used to write robot test cases over pycharm
4.configure PIP
5.Install robot framework-requests and its dependencies via PIP
            pip install -U requests
            pip install -U robotframework-requests
6.Install robotframework-jsonlibrary
            pip install jsonpath_rw
            pip install jsonpath_rw_ext
            pip install robotframework-jsonlibrary



